name: MY DEATHS
description:
my genesis on HEN
jpg 3000x2000
May this walk be like light, may I show myself, may the inopportune mouths shut up, may the mental currents be released because there is no more common sense in our days! FIGHT, my life belongs to no one, I FIGHT, opaque happiness in the intense sky.
Photography to immortalize the end and painting to make the beginning splendorous. Today I feel freedom in spirit and PLEASURE is mine...
~ Wellington Alves.
